  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Acid Trip!</h2><br><strong>ACID TRIP</strong> is a 2d top-down shooter you can play it with raw brutality, hard-boiled gunplay, and skull-crushing close combat and defeat bosses, zombies, and don't die from shredders, traps to make it more hellish and brutal. <strong>it's like if doom was 2d.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/c6c5f92777a4ceeda3ad607bd38afd62.poster.avif?t=1683699100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/c6c5f92777a4ceeda3ad607bd38afd62.webm?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/c6c5f92777a4ceeda3ad607bd38afd62.mp4?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>KILL</strong>, destroy, fuck up zombies. Oh, and look good to your friends by smashing their scores on the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/d96285d6cc5dc9bb17fd7df1a37e73c3.poster.avif?t=1683699100\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/d96285d6cc5dc9bb17fd7df1a37e73c3.webm?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/d96285d6cc5dc9bb17fd7df1a37e73c3.mp4?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY:</h2>You’ve come here for a reason. they are to friends working on new year eve so one of them put acid in <strong>candy 🍬</strong> and they took it without knowing so they took an overdose and the hungover started the game take place in their mind tripping and making them imagine they are in a zombie apocalypse and <strong>If they die in there mind they die in the real world.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/df01f8b6bc4ab6e6535e55367f0967d0.poster.avif?t=1683699100\" width=720 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/df01f8b6bc4ab6e6535e55367f0967d0.webm?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/df01f8b6bc4ab6e6535e55367f0967d0.mp4?t=1683699100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES:</h2>  <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Back-Breaking , Challenging Gameplay</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>purchase Perks and upgrades to Kill, destroy, fuck up zombies more brutality!!!<strong><br><br></strong></strong></li><li>  <strong>Endless Possibilities and a variety of powerups</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Fast-paced gameplay that will make the bones in your hands shatter!!!</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Leaderboards to prove you're better than the rest of the world, or at least your friends!</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Dodge, shoot, and destroy 8 challenging multi-form bosses</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Intense sound design with gurgling zombies and all that shit!</strong><br><br></li><li>  <strong>Intense Musical Accompaniment</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1683699100\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792810/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e25